<codeline lineno="42"><highlight class="stringliteral"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="43"><highlight class="stringliteral">The<sp/>action<sp/>can<sp/>be<sp/>used<sp/>to<sp/>play<sp/>Windows<sp/>system<sp/>sounds.<sp/>For<sp/>example::</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="44"><highlight class="stringliteral"></highlight></codeline>
