<codeline lineno="47"><highlight class="stringliteral"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="48"><highlight class="stringliteral"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>#<sp/>Play<sp/>the<sp/>logout<sp/>sound.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="49"><highlight class="stringliteral"><sp/><sp/><sp/><sp/>PlaySound(&quot;WindowsLogout&quot;).execute()</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="50"><highlight class="stringliteral"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="51"><highlight class="stringliteral"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="52"><highlight class="stringliteral">System<sp/>sound<sp/>names<sp/>are<sp/>matched<sp/>against<sp/>registry<sp/>keys.</highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="53"><highlight class="stringliteral"></highlight></codeline>
<codeline lineno="54"><highlight class="stringliteral">Invalid<sp/>file<sp/>paths<sp/>or<sp/>unknown<sp/>system<sp/>sounds<sp/>will<sp/>result<sp/>in<sp/>the<sp/>default<sp/>error</highlight></codeline>
